#: ../../talk/call_screenshare.rst:3
msgid "Screen sharing"
msgstr "Comhroinnt scáileáin"

#: ../../talk/call_screenshare.rst:5
msgid "Click the monitor icon in the toolbar to share your screen."
msgstr ""
"Cliceáil ar dheilbhín an mhonatóra sa bharra uirlisí chun do scáileán a "
"roinnt."

#: ../../talk/call_screenshare.rst:7
msgid ""
"If you have not yet given permission to the browser or the Talk Desktop "
"client to share your screen, you might be prompted to do so when you click "
"``Share screen``. Please click on ``Allow`` to grant the browser or Talk "
"Desktop client access to your screen."
msgstr ""
"Mura bhfuil cead tugtha agat fós don bhrabhsálaí nó don chliant Talk Desktop"
" do scáileán a roinnt, d’fhéadfaí iarraidh ort é sin a dhéanamh nuair a "
"chliceálann tú ar “Comhroinn scáileán”. Cliceáil ar “Ceadaigh” le rochtain a"
" thabhairt don bhrabhsálaí nó don chliant Talk Desktop ar do scáileán."

#: ../../talk/call_screenshare.rst:11
msgid ""
"Depending on your browser or the Talk Desktop client, you will get the "
"option to share a monitor, an application window, or a single browser tab. "
"If video from your camera is also available, other participants will see it "
"in a small presenter view next to the screen share."
msgstr ""
"Ag brath ar do bhrabhsálaí nó ar chliant Talk Desktop, gheobhaidh tú an "
"rogha monatóir, fuinneog feidhmchláir, nó cluaisín brabhsálaí aonair a "
"roinnt. Má tá físeán ó do cheamara ar fáil freisin, feicfidh rannpháirtithe "
"eile é i radharc beag láithreora in aice leis an gcomhroinnt scáileáin."

#: ../../talk/call_screenshare.rst:17
msgid ""
"To stop sharing your screen, click the ``Share screen`` button again and "
"choose ``Stop screensharing``."
msgstr ""
"Chun stop a chur le comhroinnt do scáileáin, cliceáil an cnaipe ``Comhroinn "
"scáileán`` arís agus roghnaigh ``Stop comhroinnt scáileáin``."

#: ../../talk/call_screenshare.rst:19
msgid ""
"You can zoom in and out of the shared screen with the mouse wheel, double-"
"click, or touchpad gestures."
msgstr ""
"Is féidir leat zúmáil isteach agus amach as an scáileán comhroinnte le roth "
"na luiche, cliceáil faoi dhó, nó gothaí an phainéil tadhaill."
